that the new fee
arrangement was hampering the company=E2=80=99s ability to compete. As we k=
now, the company did the right thing and reversed course.=C2=A0

=C2=A0

The fee structure, however, didn=E2=80=99t cause the cash squeeze=E2=80=94t=
